<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8322028>
    dc:description "Fig. 14. Roddenberryus pelegrina (Bryant, 1940) gen. nov., ♀, holotype (MCZ 22577). A. Habitus, dorsal view, white arrow showing invagination on clypeus margin, black arrows showing a dense tuft of black setae on apical part of tibia. B. Habitus, ventral view. C. Mouthparts and palps, ventral view. Scale bars: 1.0 mm. Photos taken by A. Sánchez-Ruiz at AMNH in 2002." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8322028/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8322030>
    dc:description "Fig. 15. Distribution map of Roddenberryus kirk gen. et sp. nov. (circles), R. mccoy gen. et sp. nov. (triangle), R. spock gen. et sp. nov. (heart), R. sargi (Pickard-Cambridge, 1899) comb. nov. (square) and R. pelegrina (Bryant, 1940) comb. nov. (star)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8322030/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

